&lt;li&gt;Create reference architectures and share your work through documentation, open source, community engagement, and conference presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rapidly iterate with input from colleagues and reference customers; turn customer conversations into shippable prototypes and reference designs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hold the production bar on prototypes that often graduate into Tailscale&#39;s product surface area, including the security and review practices that wrap around agent-generated code.&lt;/li&gt;
