&lt;p&gt;At Squarespace, we&#39;re reimagining how people bring their ideas to life online. Our R&amp;amp;D Engineering teams are at the heart of that mission — building the seamless, powerful experiences our customers rely on every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Backend Engineer, you&#39;ll be part of a collaborative, high-impact team working to create scalable, reliable systems behind some of the most intuitive tools on the web. Whether you&#39;ve been in the industry for three years or twenty, if you&#39;re passionate about designing elegant solutions— we want to hear from you. This is a hybrid role working from our NYC office 3 days per week. You will report to the Engineering Team Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring across several impactful R&amp;amp;D teams. Based on your experience and interests, you could join one of the following:&lt;/p&gt;
